Madematix SLiM Theme
====================

This directory contains the stuff needed to create the 'madematix-slim-theme' 
Arch package. 

Instructions
------------
1. make                              (will create the pkg in bin dir)
2. cd bin
3. pacman -U madematix-<...>.xz      (install the package)
4. cd .. && make clean               (optionally, remove bin dir)
5. In /etc/slim.config:
	
	current_theme	    madematix-slim-theme		

